          35
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-5 border">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500">
          Pass Rate
        </h3>
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mt-2">
          78%
        </p>
